OL,3,CHunt for #10.6m London lottery jackpot
OL,4,Cwinner as deadline looms
OL,6,FThe deadline is fast approaching for a
OL,7,FLondon lottery winner to claim their
OL,8,F#10,633,323 prize after matching all
OL,9,Fsix main numbers in the 4 October 2025
OL,10,Fdraw.
OL,12,FThe ticket was bought in London
OL,13,FBorough of Bexley with the winning
OL,14,Fnumbers of 06, 08, 12, 33, 49, 59. The
OL,15,Fticket expires on 2 April.
OL,17,FLottery operator Allwyn said: "Despite
OL,18,Fextensive efforts, the winner has not
OL,19,Fyet come forward, and the prize is set
OL,20,Fto expire on 2 April 2026.
